Deep Research，能连续思考半小时输出万字回复！压力给到了DeepSeek？</a>\n              <br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">\n             </section>\n             <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;padding-top: 23px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27px;visibility: visible;\">\n              <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1NDA4NjU2MA==&amp;mid=2247632506&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=af461d9a2fa00fa8e51e8b5c27531de8&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"奥特曼承认DeepSeek削弱OpenAI地位，特朗普、黄仁勋再限芯片出口；除夕给表白员工发钱，CEO称促成几对情侣｜AI周报\" linktype=\"text\" imgurl=\"\" imgdata=\"null\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-linktype=\"2\" style=\"outline: 0px;color: var(--weui-LINK);cursor: default;\">奥特曼承认DeepSeek削弱OpenAI地位，特朗普、黄仁勋再限芯片出口；除夕给表白员工发钱，CEO称促成几对情侣｜AI周报</a>\n              <br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">\n             </section>\n             <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;padding-top: 23px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27px;visibility: visible;\">\n              <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1NDA4NjU2MA==&amp;mid=2247632506&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=4621a80e36157a4cdb641f76cd17094a&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"让大模型读懂善用知识库！清华等团队推出 UltraRAG 框架全家桶\" linktype=\"text\" imgurl=\"\" imgdata=\"null\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-linktype=\"2\" style=\"outline: 0px;color: var(--weui-LINK);cursor: default;\">让大模型读懂善用知识库！清华等团队推出 UltraRAG 框架全家桶</a>\n              <br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">\n             </section>\n             <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;padding-top: 23px;pad